Comment: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:15.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,大切な落とし物を
Comment: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:18.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,知らない君が拾って
Comment: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,届けてくれたみたいな
Comment: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:24.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,思いがけない朝
Comment: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そういえば大事なものは
Comment: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:29.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ちゃんと名前を書かなくじゃ
Comment: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,どこかで失くしてしまうと
Comment: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:35.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,よく言われてたのに
Comment: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:38.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰かの　せいじゃなくて
Comment: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:41.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰かの　ものでもなくて
Comment: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,変わらず　世界は
Comment: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そこにあるよ
Comment: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,風と　さあ手と手繋いで
Comment: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,空と　息を合わせて
Comment: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:54.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,行こう　動き出した
Comment: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:58.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,心の矢印
Comment: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,君と　そう君とならば
Comment: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ならば　そう君とだから
Comment: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:12.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,何が起きるかなんかわからない未来が
Comment: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,走る
Comment: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:18.83,OPJP,last,0,0,0,karaoke,キラキラ　跳ねてる
Comment: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:31.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,OPJP End
Comment: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:01.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN Start
Comment: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:15.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我那珍貴的失物
Comment: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:18.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,被素不相識的你撿起
Comment: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,把它交還給我
Comment: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:24.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,出乎意料的清晨
Comment: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,這麼說來　重要的東西
Comment: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:29.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定要寫上名字
Comment: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然會丟失於不知何處
Comment: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:35.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,經常被這樣告誡
Comment: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:38.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是任何人的錯
Comment: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:41.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也不屬於任何人
Comment: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一成不變的世界
Comment: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,存在於此
Comment: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,隨風　來吧手牽手
Comment: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,於空　配合對方步調
Comment: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:54.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧　出發了
Comment: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:58.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,心之所向
Comment: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,與你　沒錯　如果與你一起
Comment: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯　正因為與你一起
Comment: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:12.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,向著未知的未來
Comment: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,奔跑
